# Magic Mirror Project Rules

## Project Overview
- A Next.js application that uses face recognition to create a smart mirror interface
- Built with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS
- Uses face-api.js for face detection and recognition
- Uses Prisma for database management

## Development Rules
1. All code must be written in TypeScript
2. Follow the established project structure
3. Use Tailwind CSS for styling
4. Implement proper error handling and loading states
5. Follow the execution plan phases in order
6. Test each phase before moving to the next
7. Maintain proper documentation

## Technical Requirements
- Node.js environment
- Camera access
- Modern web browser with WebRTC support
- SQLite database (for development)
